### Test VLEI Ecosystem Call Messages

# Start the chatbot API first:
# cd vlei-ecosystem-agent\vlei-chatbot-api && dotnet run

### 1. Start a new conversation
POST http://localhost:5184/api/Chat/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "initialMessage": "I'm the CEO of a company with LEI: 549300ABCDEF123456789"
}

### 2. Send a message that should trigger tool calls
POST http://localhost:5184/api/Chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Search for companies in Italy with more than 100 employees",
    "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### 3. Send another message to test different tool calls
POST http://localhost:5184/api/Chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Validate my LEI credentials and check supplier status",
    "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### 4. Test query functionality
POST http://localhost:5184/api/Chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Generate a report about companies in Lombardia region",
    "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}